reviewText: Not very helpful, very limited information.  He used only a used standard guitar neck versus a homemade neck or prefab neck for cbg.  I was looking for information on best way to cut different boxes, How high to set the neck, proper bridge placement as in exactly where to measure from (and he only demonstrated one type of bridge), planning for string height et cetera so I did it right the first time versus trying to fudge everything and make it work.  This was basically a waste of money.  Nothing here I didn't know from just researching what is free on the internet.
